opam-version: "2.0"
name: "tar-mirage"
version: "0.9.0"
synopsis: "Decode and encode tar files"
description: """
tar-format is a simple library to read and write tar files with an emphasis on
streaming.

This is pure OCaml code, no C bindings."""
